<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 14:07:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队为向英国《每日邮报》提供不为人知的人质绑架信息而道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/israeli-army-gave-british-daily-mail-information-on-hostages-kidnapping-unknown-to-family/0000018f-aa2f-d8a2-a3cf-aeaf68c90000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人道歉并表示，“人为错误”是罪魁祸首，此前以色列军队向英国报纸提供了材料，其中载有以色列马坦·赞高克被哈马斯恐怖分子绑架的细节，而该家人此前并不知道这些细节。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 11:35:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/israeli-army-gave-british-daily-mail-information-on-hostages-kidnapping-unknown-to-family/0000018f-aa2f-d8a2-a3cf-aeaf68c90000</guid></item><item><title>承认巴勒斯坦国后，以色列外长切断西班牙大使馆与约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人之间的联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/israel-cuts-off-spanish-embassy-from-providing-services-to-west-bank-palestinians/0000018f-aa11-df13-a3af-be17e3620000</link><description>外交部长以色列·卡茨表示，以色列将“切断西班牙在以色列的代表权与巴勒斯坦人之间的联系”，以回应西班牙承认巴勒斯坦国以及该国副总理的反犹太主义言论。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 11:01:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/israel-cuts-off-spanish-embassy-from-providing-services-to-west-bank-palestinians/0000018f-aa11-df13-a3af-be17e3620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队打捞出三名人质的尸体，三名人质于 10 月 7 日被杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-recover-bodies-of-three-hostages-held-in-gaza-killed-on-october-7/0000018f-a976-d0b4-a3cf-bf7e034d0000</link><description>军方表示，这三人是在哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列领土期间或在他们被带入加沙地道之前被杀的。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 09:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-recover-bodies-of-three-hostages-held-in-gaza-killed-on-october-7/0000018f-a976-d0b4-a3cf-bf7e034d0000</guid></item><item><title>受害者和加害者：电影如何让以色列人处理他们压抑的集体创伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/victim-and-victimizer-how-film-lets-israelis-process-their-repressed-collective-trauma/0000018f-a8b2-df13-a3af-bcb6c2630000</link><description>以色列电影如何处理该国的民族伤疤？为什么大屠杀和大灾难不断出现在战争电影中？董事们将如何应对 10 月 7 日的影响？</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 04:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/victim-and-victimizer-how-film-lets-israelis-process-their-repressed-collective-trauma/0000018f-a8b2-df13-a3af-bcb6c2630000</guid></item><item><title>“战争让我的妻子想要为在以色列的生活而更加努力地奋斗。我的感觉正好相反’</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-24/ty-article/.highlight/the-war-made-my-wife-want-to-fight-harder-for-life-in-israel-i-feel-the-opposite-way/0000018f-a898-dfc6-a3ef-bddc1c000000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对夫妇在面对战争时试图决定如何度过自己的生活，而一名年轻人则试图找出如何以他喜欢的事情为中心的日常生活</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-24/ty-article/.highlight/the-war-made-my-wife-want-to-fight-harder-for-life-in-israel-i-feel-the-opposite-way/0000018f-a898-dfc6-a3ef-bddc1c000000</guid></item><item><title>“观众比其他人更关心这场冲突”：美联社高级编辑关于加沙战争报道的采访</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/audiences-care-more-about-this-conflict-than-others-ap-top-editor-on-gaza-war-coverage/0000018f-a6b7-d8a2-a3cf-a6b7a0f10000</link><description>美联社正面临 10 月 7 日受害者家属的诉讼，指控该通讯社对袭击事件发出了预先警告，并声称其对加沙战争和以色列通讯部长袭击事件的报道存在偏见。在一次内容广泛的采访中，执行编辑朱莉·佩斯反驳了这些指控</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:14:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/audiences-care-more-about-this-conflict-than-others-ap-top-editor-on-gaza-war-coverage/0000018f-a6b7-d8a2-a3cf-a6b7a0f10000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府231天的失败。我们到哪儿了？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/231-days-of-failures-by-netanyahus-government-where-did-we-get-to/0000018f-a6cb-d476-a7df-e7eb4b680000</link><description>由于欧洲大门对他和他的妻子关闭，他担心被指控为战犯，这让内塔尼亚胡失眠的时间比人质的命运还要多。 他恳求美国政府把他从海牙救出来，但准备在拜登的演讲背后发表演讲回到美国国会</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/231-days-of-failures-by-netanyahus-government-where-did-we-get-to/0000018f-a6cb-d476-a7df-e7eb4b680000</guid></item><item><title>被俘女士兵的镜头给以色列及其冷酷的总理蒙上了阴影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/footage-of-captive-female-soldiers-casts-a-toxic-cloud-over-israel-and-its-callous-pm/0000018f-a6bc-d24f-a5df-fefec78b0000</link><description>尽管有女兵被扣为人质的悲惨视频，但内塔尼亚胡不会推进协议 ■ 美国现在不再那么反对拉法行动，以色列正在推进 — — 但不是为了击败哈马斯</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/footage-of-captive-female-soldiers-casts-a-toxic-cloud-over-israel-and-its-callous-pm/0000018f-a6bc-d24f-a5df-fefec78b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列已经夷平了这个贝都因村庄的数百所房屋。接下来，它撕毁了所有剩下的东西</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-razed-hundreds-of-homes-in-this-bedouin-village-next-it-tore-down-their-tents/0000018f-a6ed-d1e2-a1ff-aeef40370000</link><description>反对拆除哈利勒干河运动的领导人之一贾布尔·阿布·阿萨说，“当局的行为就像西岸的山顶青年”</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-razed-hundreds-of-homes-in-this-bedouin-village-next-it-tore-down-their-tents/0000018f-a6ed-d1e2-a1ff-aeef40370000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院命令以色列立即停止在拉法的行动，理由是人道主义局势“灾难性”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-deliver-decision-on-emergency-measures-against-israel/0000018f-a694-d476-a7df-e7fd24770000</link><description>如果以色列违反世界法院停止战争或拉法军事行动的命令，它可能会面临国际制裁。尽管美国预计会在这种情况下支持以色列，但大多数西方政府可能会支持法院的裁决</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-deliver-decision-on-emergency-measures-against-israel/0000018f-a694-d476-a7df-e7fd24770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队从加沙打捞出 10 月 7 日被杀的三名人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-live/netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-u-s-congress-trump-many-israeli-hostages-are-dead/0000018f-a83e-d8a2-a3cf-acbfde440000</link><description>《纽约时报》：中央情报局和摩萨德领导人将在欧洲会面，讨论重启加沙谈判 ■ 黎巴嫩报道：以色列无人机在该国南部击中汽车 ■ 战斗机拦截接近以色列的无人机，在萨法德附近引发火灾 ■ 国际法院将就紧急措施作出决定反对以色列 ■ 内塔尼亚胡将在美国国会联席会议上发表讲话</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 01:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-live/netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-u-s-congress-trump-many-israeli-hostages-are-dead/0000018f-a83e-d8a2-a3cf-acbfde440000</guid></item><item><title>“让你的学校难堪”：大学领导因屈服于“亲哈马斯”团体而受到共和党议员的欺凌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/university-leaders-get-bullied-by-republican-lawmakers-for-caving-in-to-pro-hamas-groups/0000018f-a735-dfc6-a3ef-b77d24480000</link><description>在三个多小时的艰苦审讯中，西北大学、罗格斯大学和加州大学洛杉矶分校的校长因没有更强有力地镇压在校园内未经授权设立营地的反以色列抗议者而受到严厉批评。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 21:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/university-leaders-get-bullied-by-republican-lawmakers-for-caving-in-to-pro-hamas-groups/0000018f-a735-dfc6-a3ef-b77d24480000</guid></item><item><title>国会接待内塔尼亚胡并不是“亲以色列”，内塔尼亚胡被半数以上的国家鄙视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-23/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-pro-israel-for-congress-to-host-netanyahu-despised-more-than-half-his-country/0000018f-a665-d476-a7df-e76d6bb70000</link><description>在国会面前发表讲话只是内塔尼亚胡宁愿做的另一件事，而不是面对 10 月 7 日之前遭受毁灭性打击的以色列人</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 19:47:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-23/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-pro-israel-for-congress-to-host-netanyahu-despised-more-than-half-his-country/0000018f-a665-d476-a7df-e76d6bb70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁同意继续与哈马斯进行人质谈判，但消息人士对谈判是否成功表示怀疑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-okays-continuation-of-talks-with-hamas-as-sources-doubtful-of-success/0000018f-a651-d8a2-a3cf-a6d394090000</link><description>熟悉战时内阁部长讨论情况的消息人士称，谈判小组有一定的回旋余地，但很快达成协议释放人质的可能性很低</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 17:59:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-okays-continuation-of-talks-with-hamas-as-sources-doubtful-of-success/0000018f-a651-d8a2-a3cf-a6d394090000</guid></item><item><title>参议员乔什·霍利：关于共和党、以色列和反犹太主义的案例研究</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sen-josh-hawley-a-case-study-on-the-republicans-israel-and-antisemitism/0000018f-a591-d1e2-a1ff-afbf050f0000</link><description>自2018年当选以来，这位密苏里州参议员已经从持有传统的鹰派观点，转变为唐纳德·特朗普和塔克·卡尔森倡导的孤立主义“美国优先”方针。不过，他对反犹太主义比喻的使用更加一致</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 17:26:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sen-josh-hawley-a-case-study-on-the-republicans-israel-and-antisemitism/0000018f-a591-d1e2-a1ff-afbf050f0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人对西班牙、爱尔兰和挪威的国家承认感到高兴，但也有些愤世嫉俗。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-react-with-joy-and-some-cynicism-to-state-recognition-by-european-countries/0000018f-a5ac-d0b4-a3cf-b7ace61a0000</link><description>尽管巴勒斯坦官方渠道感谢挪威、爱尔兰和西班牙承认巴勒斯坦国的决定，但网上的一些人提出了更多质疑</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 17:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-react-with-joy-and-some-cynicism-to-state-recognition-by-european-countries/0000018f-a5ac-d0b4-a3cf-b7ace61a0000</guid></item><item><title>英国提前大选意味着英国犹太人和穆斯林将度过丑陋的六周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/u-k-snap-election-means-six-ugly-weeks-for-british-jews-and-muslims/0000018f-a60f-d9c2-af8f-b7df4e7e0000</link><description>下届英国大选结果对加沙战争的影响力为零。但保守党和极左翼都希望通过将其注入竞选活动中，向工党领袖凯尔·斯塔默施加压力，并使穆斯林选民反对他</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 17:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/u-k-snap-election-means-six-ugly-weeks-for-british-jews-and-muslims/0000018f-a60f-d9c2-af8f-b7df4e7e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 230 天：埃及消息人士称，以色列仍未准备好进行人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-230-israel-still-not-ready-for-hostage-deal-egyptian-source-says/0000018f-a655-d476-a7df-e77d73380001</link><description>战时内阁指示以色列谈判团队与哈马斯进行进一步谈判 ■ 以色列国防军调查发现，以色列军队上周在加沙无意中杀害了联合国援助人员 ■ 以色列国防军表示，2023 年 3 月至 7 月期间，内塔尼亚胡总理收到了来自军事情报部门的四份单独的书面警告，称以色列的内部危机鼓励伊朗、真主党和哈马斯采取行动反对它 ■ 这是战争 230 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 16:51:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-230-israel-still-not-ready-for-hostage-deal-egyptian-source-says/0000018f-a655-d476-a7df-e77d73380001</guid></item><item><title>十月后，与犹太以色列人相比，阿拉伯以色列人患创伤后应激障碍、焦虑和抑郁的风险更大。 7、研究发现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/arabs-at-greater-risk-of-ptsd-compared-to-jews-in-israel-post-oct-7-study-finds/0000018f-a605-d1e2-a1ff-ae2f49440000</link><description>鲁宾学术中心的研究人员发现，与犹太人相比，阿拉伯人患 PTSD 的可能性高出约 2.5 倍，患抑郁症的可能性高出约 1.7 倍，患焦虑症的可能性高出 6.4 倍</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 16:21:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/arabs-at-greater-risk-of-ptsd-compared-to-jews-in-israel-post-oct-7-study-finds/0000018f-a605-d1e2-a1ff-ae2f49440000</guid></item><item><title>当这些以色列士兵在加沙死亡时，他们的同性恋身份也随之消失</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-these-israeli-soldiers-died-in-gaza-their-gay-identity-died-with-them/0000018f-9fc1-da35-a3af-dfeb78f20000</link><description>“诺姆的家人只是想埋葬一切，隐藏他的身份和身份”：他们的同性恋伴侣在加沙的死亡意味着这些失去亲人的伴侣必须独自应对这一损失，没有周围人或国家的支持</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 15:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-these-israeli-soldiers-died-in-gaza-their-gay-identity-died-with-them/0000018f-9fc1-da35-a3af-dfeb78f20000</guid></item></channel></rss>